### Steps to reproduce
Set listener for window.onpopstate and navigate through VUE app using VUE router. Event is never fired. Demo: https://jsfiddle.net/bjb8ukb8/ Event popstate works correctly without VUE. Demo: https://jsfiddle.net/bzo67L32/2/

